### ==================== 1. 上传资源 ====================

### 1.1 上传PDF课件资源
# @name uploadPdfResource
POST {{baseUrl}}/resource/upload
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{uploaderToken}}

{
  "title": "数据结构与算法 - 期末复习资料",
  "description": "包含所有章节的知识点总结、经典例题和历年真题解析。适合期末复习使用。",
  "fileUrl": "https://campuslink-oss.example.com/resources/data-structure-review.pdf",
  "fileName": "数据结构期末复习.pdf",
  "fileSize": 5242880,
  "fileType": "pdf",
  "category": "课件",
  "courseName": "数据结构与算法",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "score": 5
}

