### ==================== 2. 获取资源列表 ====================

### 2.1 获取所有资源列表（默认分页）
# @name getAllResources
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.2 获取资源列表（指定分页参数）
# @name getResourcesWithPagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?page=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.3 按分类筛选 - 课件
# @name getResourcesByCategory
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?category=课件&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.4 按分类筛选 - 试题
# @name getExamResources
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?category=试题
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.5 按分类筛选 - 笔记
# @name getNoteResources
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?category=笔记
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.6 按学校筛选
# @name getResourcesBySchool
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?schoolId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.7 按下载量排序（降序）
# @name getResourcesSortedByDownloads
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?sortBy=downloads&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.8 按积分排序（升序）
# @name getResourcesSortedByScore
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?sortBy=score&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

### 2.9 组合筛选：课件 + 学校1 + 按时间降序
# @name getResourcesWithFilters
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list?category=课件&schoolId=1&sortBy=created_at&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}

