### 14.2 管理员查看待审核列表
# @name rejectFlow2Pending
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 14.3 管理员拒绝资源
# @name rejectFlow3Reject
PUT {{baseUrl}}/resource/17/reject
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "rejectReason": "资源质量不达标，内容过于简单，不具备分享价值。建议补充详细内容后重新提交。"
}

### 14.4 上传者查看自己的资源（应该看到拒绝状态和原因）
# @name rejectFlow4MyList
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/my
Authorization: Bearer {{uploaderToken}}

### 14.5 在公开列表中查询（不应该看到被拒绝的资源）
# @name rejectFlow5PublicList
GET {{baseUrl}}/resource/list
Authorization: Bearer {{downloaderToken1}}
